{
  "texts": [
    "Whilst state-of-the-art in terms of accuracy, HC α scales poorly.",
    "A range of improvements to make HIVE-COTE more usable were introduced in HIVE-COTE v1.0 (HC1) (Bagnall et al., 2020a).",
    "HC1 has four modules instead of the five used in HIVE-COTE α: it drops the computationally intensive EE algorithm without loss of accuracy.",
    "BOSS is replaced by the more configurable cBOSS (Middlehurst et al. 2019).",
    "The improved randomised version of STC (Bostrom and Bagnall 2017) is included with a default limit on the search and the Rotation Forest classifier."
  ]
}